pageContext.claim: ““Federal Judge throws out Stormy Danials lawsuit versus Trump. Trump is entitled to full legal fees.” @FoxNews Great, now I can go after Horseface and her 3rd rate lawyer in the Great State of Texas. She will confirm the letter she signed! pageContext.analysis: This is another exaggeration connected to Trump's relationship with Stormy Daniels. They had met, knew each other and Trump made a payment via his lawyer to Daniels before the 2016 election in an effort to stop her from telling her story.
